---
const today = new Date();
---

<footer class="bg-gray-900 text-gray-400 mt-16">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      <!-- Brand -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-amber-400 font-bold text-lg mb-3">Pickleball Mania</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Le site francophone de reference sur le pickleball. Actualites, tests, conseils et guides d'equipement.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Navigation -->
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-white font-semibold mb-3">Navigation</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/blog/" class="hover:text-amber-400 transition-colors">Actualites</a></li>
          <li><a href="/categorie/tests/" class="hover:text-amber-400 transition-colors">Tests & Avis</a></li>
          <li><a href="/categorie/conseils/" class="hover:text-amber-400 transition-colors">Conseils</a></li>
          <li><a href="/equipement/" class="hover:text-amber-400 transition-colors">Equipement</a></li>
          <li><a href="/categorie/debuter/" class="hover:text-amber-400 transition-colors">Debuter</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Legal -->
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-white font-semibold mb-3">Informations</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/about/" class="hover:text-amber-400 transition-colors">A propos</a></li>
          <li><a href="/mentions-legales/" class="hover:text-amber-400 transition-colors">Mentions legales</a></li>
          <li><a href="/politique-confidentialite/" class="hover:text-amber-400 transition-colors">Confidentialite</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Affiliate -->
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-white font-semibold mb-3">Partenaire</h4>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed">
          En tant que Partenaire Amazon, nous realisons un benefice sur les achats remplissant les conditions requises.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-gray-800 mt-8 pt-6 text-center text-sm">
      <p>&copy; {today.getFullYear()} Pickleball Mania. Tous droits reserves.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
